		<title>Ethereum DeFi Regulations&#058; Navigating the Legal Complexities</title>
		<link>https://securenest.org/learn/ethereum-defi-regulations</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Jordan Adams]]></dc:creator>
