<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Key Takeaways</h2>



<ul>
<li>Ethereum DeFi staking offers the potential for an annual return of 10%.</li>



<li>Staking Ethereum allows individuals to earn passive income and diversify their investment portfolio.</li>



