<li><strong>Peer-to-Peer Transactions</strong>: DeFi platforms enable direct peer-to-peer transactions without the need for intermediaries. This reduces costs and eliminates the barriers that traditional financial systems impose, making financial services more affordable and accessible to individuals of all income levels.</li>



<li><strong>Programmable Money</strong>: Ethereum DeFi platforms offer programmable money through smart contracts. This allows users to create and execute financial agreements automatically, without relying on third parties. Programmable money enables greater efficiency, transparency, and trust in financial transactions, benefitting individuals and businesses alike.</li>
</ol>



